
This directory contains the following files:

literature:
	README		: this file
	espel.help	: brief summary of commands
	espel.l		: manual page
shell scripts:
	INSTALL		: sets file variables in espel and makefile 
	espel		: this script coordinates spell, espel.hi, etc.
source files:
	makefile	: make will compile and install
	*.[ch]		: c source and macro files
These two files are created from the source files
	espel.hi	: human interface, a.out format
	spellin		: creates a hash table for spell

be sure to read makefile and INSTALL
To install type:
		INSTALL
		make install

